OL,5, Retail sales volumes fell by 3.2% in   
OL,6, December in the sharpest drop since the
OL,7, UK was in a Covid lockdown.            
OL,9,FOfficial figures revealed a sharp fall 
OL,10,Fin demand for goods, but food sales    
OL,11,Falso declined in the run-up to         
OL,12,FChristmas.                             
OL,14,FThe Office for National Statistics     
OL,15,F(ONS) said it appeared people did their
OL,16,Fshopping earlier in November, taking   
OL,17,Fadvantage of Black Friday sales.       
OL,19,FIt meant that retail sales tumbled at  
OL,20,Fthe fastest rate since January 2021.   
